# Weather Classifier App (Expo React Native)

Application uses your phone camera or photos to detect weather conditions

---

## Setup

Install:
- Node.js (v18+)
- Git
- Expo Go App

## Get Project

**Clone Repo**

```bash
git clone <repo-url>
cd WeatherClassifier
```

## Install Dependencies

```
npm install @react-navigation/native @react-navigation/stack @react-navigation/bottom-tabs
npx expo install react-native-screens react-native-safe-area-context
npx expo install expo-camera expo-image-picker expo-media-library
npx expo install @react-native-async-storage/async-storage
```

---

## Run The App

```bash
npx expo start
```

Then:
- Open Expo Go on your phone OR Open the Camera Application
- Scan the QR Code

